	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Oct 29th 6:59 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>We killed the Black Dire last night after taking out the Advisor. Group helping with Epic included.<br><br>2 Groups about 4 or 5 in each<br>50 Shaman myself (Healed Buffed, used Pet)<br>51 Druid (Healed Buffed)<br>50 Druid (Healed Buffed)<br>44 Druid (Healed)<br>36 Druid (Healed)<br>48 Warrior (Tanked)<br>47 Warrior (Tanked<br>52 Warrior (Tanked)<br>51 Warrior (Tanked)<br>46 Ranger (Tanked)<br><br>Ranger used Harmony on all the wolves... 52 Warrior pulled Black Dire with Arrow to group. After a few failed attempts to snare by the Druids and few failed attempt to Malo/Slow by myself... we just healed the Tanks when necessary. 52 Warrior was taking most of the beating and none of the Tanks lost over a bubble of health.<br>Black Dire wolf went down fairly quick despite all the resists. Overpowering and brute force seemed to work best.<br><br>I did hear from the group I was in that a lvl 58 Shaman soloed the Black Dire Wolf with some difficulty.   <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
