	   <tr><td colspan=2>We were able to take out the Black Dire with 1 group, and only one person was over 50. <br><br>53 Druid (Pulled, took HT)<br>45 Monk (Main Tank)<br>45 Ranger (Backup Tank)<br>45 Enchanter (DeBuff/Haste)<br>40 Shaman (DeBuff/DoT/Buff)<br>35 Cleric (Healed)<br><br>The Dire dropped much easier than expected. Only had to heal Monk once or twice with Superior heal from Cleric. My group spent half the day in Mistmoore collecting different pieces for multiple quests. The Black Dire was on the top of our list. With this one group, we owned the Zone. A majority of the time, we were the only players in the zone as well. <br><br>Lgurin<br>42 Barbarian Shaman<br>E'Ci Server<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Dec  4 01:57:54 2001</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Oddloots Barginbins, <br>The best prices in Norrath!</td></tr>
